long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Download Shein product images and videos easily with this popular tool!
Click once to save Shein images in high quality directly to your computer. Simple and efficient!

⭐ **Getting Started:**

🚀 Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension.
🛍️ Open your target Shein product page.
📸 Click on the Shein Image Downloader icon to open it.
📥 Download product images by variants, main, and description.
📊 Export images and video details to Excel.

⭐ **Features:**

❤️free
🗂️ Download Images Individually (*.jpeg)

💎pro
🖼️ One Click Download Images (*.zip,*.xlsx)
🎥 Download Videos (*.mp4, *.xlsx)

❓ **Why Choose Shein Image Downloader?**

⚡ Fast and easy way to download Shein product images and videos.
📝 Export product information including sku,color, productName, Image URLs directly to Excel.
📈 Perfect for sellers, researchers, and anyone needing to save product details from Shein.

📬 **Contact Us:**
Please do not hesitate to contact us with any questions at 📧 webstarue@gmail.com.
